## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="25572-197">如果当前<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>表示泛型方法定义，然后：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-197">If the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> represents a generic method definition, then:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="25572-198">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` 返回 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-198">`IsGenericMethodDefinition` returns `true`.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="25572-199">每个<xref:System.Type>中返回的数组对象<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments>方法：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-199">For each <xref:System.Type> object in the array returned by the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.GetGenericArguments> method:</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="25572-200"><xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> 属性返回 `true`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-200">The <xref:System.Type.IsGenericParameter?displayProperty=nameWithType> property returns `true`.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="25572-201"><xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType>返回当前<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-201">The <xref:System.Type.DeclaringMethod?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns the current <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>.</span></span>

      - <span data-ttu-id="25572-202"><xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性是相同的位置<xref:System.Type>数组中的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-202">The <xref:System.Type.GenericParameterPosition?displayProperty=nameWithType> property is the same as the position of the <xref:System.Type> object in the array.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="25572-203">使用`IsGenericMethodDefinition`属性以确定是否已将类型参数分配给泛型方法的类型参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-203">Use the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property to determine whether type arguments have been assigned to the type parameters of a generic method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-204">如果已分配类型参数，`IsGenericMethodDefinition`属性返回 false，即使某些类型参数是<xref:System.Type>表示类型参数的封闭类型的对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-204">If type arguments have been assigned, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false even if some of the type arguments are <xref:System.Type> objects that represent type parameters of enclosing types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-205">例如，考虑以下 C\#，Visual Basic 和C++代码：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-205">For example, consider the following C\#, Visual Basic, and C++ code:</span></span>

    ```cs
    class C
    {
        T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}
        public V M<V>(V v)
        {
            return N<V,int>(v, 42);
        }
    }
    ```

    ```vb
    Class C
        Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T
            ...
        End Function
        Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V
            Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    ref class C
    {
    private:
        generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}
    public:
        generic <typename V> V M(V v)
        {
            return N<V, int>(v, 42);
        }
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="25572-206">M 的方法体包含 N，M 和类型的类型参数指定方法的调用<xref:System.Int32>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-206">The method body of M contains a call to method N, specifying the type parameter of M and the type <xref:System.Int32>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-207">`IsGenericMethodDefinition`属性返回 false 方法`N<V,int>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-207">The `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns false for method `N<V,int>`.</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="25572-208">尽管打开构造方法`N<V,int>`是未遇到反射类 C 时，它必须生成使用<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>为了发出动态类为 C。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-208">Although the open constructed method `N<V,int>` is not encountered when reflecting over class C, it must be generated using <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> in order to emit C as a dynamic class.</span></span>


<span data-ttu-id="25572-209">如果泛型方法定义包括声明类型的泛型参数，将有一个泛型方法定义特定于每个构造的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-209">If a generic method definition includes generic parameters of the declaring type, there will be a generic method definition specific to each constructed type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-210">例如，考虑以下 C\#和 Visual Basic 代码：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-210">For example, consider the following C\# and Visual Basic code:</span></span>

    ```csharp
    class B<U,V> {}
    class C<T> { public B<T,S> M<S>() {...}}
    ```

    ```vb
    Class B(Of U, V)
    End Class
    Class C(Of T)
        Public Function M(Of S)() As B(Of T, S)
            ...
        End Function
    End Class
    ```

    ```cpp
    generic <typename U, typename V> ref class B {};
    generic <typename T> ref class C
    {
    public:
        generic <typename S> B<T,S>^ M() {...};
    };
    ```

<span data-ttu-id="25572-211">中的构造类型`C<int>`(`C(Of Integer)`在 Visual Basic 中)，返回泛型方法 M `B<int, S>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-211">In the constructed type `C<int>` (`C(Of Integer)` in Visual Basic), the generic method M returns `B<int, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-212">在开放类型`C<T>`，M 返回`B<T, S>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-212">In the open type `C<T>`, M returns `B<T, S>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-213">在这两种情况下，`IsGenericMethodDefinition`属性返回`true`为<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>表示 M。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-213">In both cases, the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property returns `true` for the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> that represents M.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="25572-214">有关特定于泛型方法的术语的固定条件列表，请参阅<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-214">For a list of the invariant conditions for terms specific to generic methods, see the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.IsGenericMethod> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-215">有关泛型反射中使用其他术语的固定条件列表，请参阅<xref:System.Type.IsGenericType>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-215">For a list of the invariant conditions for other terms used in generic reflection, see the <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType> property.</span></span>

## Examples  
<span data-ttu-id="25572-216">下面的代码示例使用`IsGenericMethodDefinition`属性来显示一个消息，指示是否<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>表示泛型方法定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-216">The following code example uses the `IsGenericMethodDefinition` property to display a message indicating whether a <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> represents a generic method definition.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="25572-217">此示例摘自一个更大的示例为提供<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-217">This example is part of a larger example provided for the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method.</span></span>

