## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="25572-223"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>方法，可编写代码，将特定类型分配给类型参数的泛型方法定义，从而创建<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>对象，表示特定的构造的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-223">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method allows you to write code that assigns specific types to the type parameters of a generic method definition, thus creating a <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object that represents a particular constructed method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-224">如果<xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A>属性的这<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo>对象返回`true`，您可以使用它来调用该方法或创建一个委托来调用该方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-224">If the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> property of this <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo> object returns `true`, you can use it to invoke the method or to create a delegate to invoke the method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="25572-225">方法用来构造<xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A>方法可以是开放的也就是说，一些其类型参数可以是封闭泛型类型的类型参数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-225">Methods constructed with the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodInfo.MakeGenericMethod%2A> method can be open, that is, some of their type arguments can be type parameters of enclosing generic types.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-226">生成动态程序集时，可能会使用此类打开的构造的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-226">You might use such open constructed methods when you generate dynamic assemblies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-227">例如，请考虑以下C#，Visual Basic 和C++代码。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-227">For example, consider the following C#, Visual Basic, and C++ code.</span></span>  
  
```  
class C  
{  
    T N<T,U>(T t, U u) {...}  
    public V M<V>(V v)  
    {  
        return N<V,int>(v, 42);  
    }  
}  
  
Class C  
    Public Function N(Of T,U)(ByVal ta As T, ByVal ua As U) As T  
        ...  
    End Function  
    Public Function M(Of V)(ByVal va As V ) As V  
        Return N(Of V, Integer)(va, 42)  
    End Function  
End Class  
  
ref class C  
{  
private:  
    generic <typename T, typename U> T N(T t, U u) {...}  
public:  
    generic <typename V> V M(V v)  
    {  
        return N<V, int>(v, 42);  
    }  
};  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="25572-228">方法体`M`包含对方法的调用`N`，指定的类型参数`M`并键入<xref:System.Int32>。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-228">The method body of `M` contains a call to method `N`, specifying the type parameter of `M` and the type <xref:System.Int32>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-229"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethodDefinition%2A>属性返回`false`方法`N<V,int>`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-229">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethodDefinition%2A> property returns `false` for method `N<V,int>`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-230"><xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A>属性返回`true`，因此方法`N<V,int>`不能调用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-230">The <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.ContainsGenericParameters%2A> property returns `true`, so method `N<V,int>` cannot be invoked.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="25572-231">有关特定于泛型方法的术语的固定条件列表，请参阅<xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethod%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-231">For a list of the invariant conditions for terms specific to generic methods, see the <xref:System.Reflection.MethodBase.IsGenericMethod%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="25572-232">有关泛型反射中使用其他术语的固定条件列表，请参阅<xref:System.Type.IsGenericType%2A>属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="25572-232">For a list of the invariant conditions for other terms used in generic reflection, see the <xref:System.Type.IsGenericType%2A> property.</span></span>  
  
   
  
